channel.title: Nancy Drew calls you!
channel.description:
Lol my sister was looking at this, and then my cell phone rang.
You enter who ever you want to calls state, and other things about them. She calls (robot lol) and mentions all of the things, and you get pretty freaked when she knows everything about you.
http://www.nancydrewcallsyou.com/
Try it on your girlfriend or something.
